name: Vitagen
description: Vitagen is an oral nutritional supplement milk powder and formulated meal replacement enriched with nutrients, calcium, vitamins and minerals. Maliban Brand "Vitagen" Nutritional Supplementary Powder is formulated under the Australian Standards of Formulated Meal Replacement and Formulated Supplemented Foods - (Standard 2.9.3). Vitagen helps to Maintain Overall Health, Provide Immune System Support and Boost Energy. It also helps to Reduce The Risks of Illness and Age-related Conditions. Improved Performance In Physical Activities and Mental Wellbeing. Supports The Healing Process During Illness/Recovery. *Images for illustration purposes only. Product received may vary.
